           fujinx

Fujifilm X Series camera tools

Usage: fj <COMMAND>

Commands:
  camera   Manage connected cameras
  convert  Convert RAF files to JPEG
  recipe   Manage recipes
  repo     Manage recipe repos
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
